reviewText: In this movie you will listen to the voices of the Anasazi Indians and see histroic pictures of them you will learn how they plant,hunt,and made things in A very simple way of life!

This is a park service video that was used many years ago in Chaco Canyon.  The video is interesting and gives details on the Anasazi.  If you haven't been to Chaco make vacation plans to visit- it is incredible!
